this project is used for geting pictures and vedios in wechat group chat by the package itchat.
Before excuting the main.py， please install python3 and the pacakage itchat.
after exucting ths main.py, there will be a 2-D code appear in the screen, scane it by your wechat scanner --to confirm login in wechat by your pc
main.py will create directroys and html files，when you and your chat-group friends send a jpg，png，mp4 file in your any chatgroup

this is my 1st git project ，enjoy it, and edit it as your like!
